text.section:
The Director shall:
Report directly to the Board;
Recommend the appointment by the Board of employees necessary for the efficient administration of the Center;
Recommend the discharge of employees for good cause and in accordance with applicable laws and policies;
Be responsible to the Board for the conduct of the Center and for its administration and supervision;
Attend all meetings of the Board, except those involving the Director's personal position;
Subject to the policies and guidelines of the Commission:
Develop a mission statement;
Submit the mission statement to the Board of Governors of the Center; and
Upon the direction of the Board of Governors, update the mission statement every 4 years; and
Perform other duties as assigned by the Board.
